The paper deals with a problem in number theory and combinatorics, specifically the Erd\H{o}s discrepancy conjecture. The techniques used involve combinatorial and number theoretic arguments, and the paper provides constructions and bounds for completely multiplicative sequences. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.GT (Discrete Mathematics), and cs.NT (Number Theory).
